			<ns0:name>pol...@google.com</ns0:name><ns0:uri>/u/101953680983947802512/</ns0:uri></ns0:author><ns0:content type="html">All the code has been written with the assumption that it will run on the main thread using the main channel. So the behavior off the main thread is unpredictable and likely to cause crashes.

We must make it a no-op for void functions; return failure otherwise. Use PPB_Core::IsMainThread().
Extend the test for each interface with a test case that starts another thread and calls each function off it.
